rigins, Jewish Americans looked east to understand themselves as Westerners.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 0aJewszUnited StatesxAttitudes toward Israel. 0aOrientalism. 0aVisual communication. 4aArea Studies : Israel Studies. 4aFilm, Visual Culture, and Performing Arts : Art. 4aHistory : American History. 4aJewish Studies : Jewish Studies. 4aReligion and Spirituality : Religion. 7aRELIGION / Judaism / History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2020z978311149149340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143848084840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438480848423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438480848/original  a978-3-11-149149-3  SUNY Press eBook Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles